{"tid":2325523,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港珠澳大橋香港口岸4名分判商夜班清潔員工確診","createTime":"2020-12-14T15:45:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T15:45:34.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a2dad1c9413adc6d1cb5a48d63ba6c8be669f1c7","tid":2325523,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T15:45:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1565257-20201214.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1565257-20201214.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=4UWfeJE2Id0Ic3Ynx8r7nyKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=99c92342\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1565257-20201214.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c39c5aeb\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1565257-20201214.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n港珠澳大橋香港口岸4名分判商夜班清潔員工，確診新型肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n他們負責港珠澳大橋香港口岸旅檢大樓的一般清潔及消毒工作，一名清潔員工首先在上周四確診後，分判商全面清潔及消毒，政府產業署說會留意事態發展，與衞生防護中心保持聯繫，配合檢疫措施。"}]}